"text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"This provider should be integrated as a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllControlItemComponentTokensProvider"},{"text":" implementation inside ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":" so as to provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":" implementation to use.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Custom themes can use subclass of ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"text":" and apply the provider they need.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It implements also the protocol ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ControlItemComponentTokens"},{"text":" so as to expose the component tokens for control-item-layout-basded components through any ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Such components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"text":"),","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"borders (from ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"),  colors (from ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":")  and spaces (from ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":").","type":"text"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"ro